      <div class="context-text">
        <p>Edgeview Finance serves manufacturing and logistics businesses across Yatala Enterprise Area, Stapylton, Pimpama, and the broader northern Gold Coast industrial corridor. Our primary focus encompasses Queensland's largest industrial precinct (Yatala) and adjacent Stapylton industrial estates, with extended coverage across Ormeau, Beenleigh, and Logan's manufacturing districts.</p>

        <p>As a local equipment finance broker, we understand Yatala's unique industrial dynamics, major employers, and equipment requirements specific to manufacturing and logistics operations. Our service area follows the Pacific Motorway M1 corridor from Brisbane to Gold Coast, targeting industrial estates, enterprise areas, and manufacturing precincts rather than retail or commercial zones.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: Finance Solutions -->
