    <div class="container-default">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        Equipment Finance and Business Funding Solutions
      </h2>

      <div class="section-intro">
        <p>Equipment finance priority reflects Yatala's 28% manufacturing workforce concentration. We focus exclusively on manufacturing, logistics, and heavy industrial operations, navigating over 40 specialist lenders to secure competitive equipment finance rates. Simple consultation process tailored to Yatala Enterprise Area industrial equipment requirements.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card-grid">
        <ServiceCard
          icon="Tool"
          title="Manufacturing & Logistics Equipment Finance"
          descriptions={[
            "Finance the equipment that drives your manufacturing or logistics operation in Yatala. From heavy machinery and forklifts to production lines and commercial vehicles, we specialise in equipment finance for Queensland's largest industrial precinct. Access over 40 specialist equipment lenders to secure competitive rates for manufacturing equipment, warehouse systems, and commercial transport that preserve your working capital.",
            "Benefits: Preserve working capital for business operations • Tax benefits (depreciation and interest deductions) • Fixed repayments for predictable cash flow management • Asset ownership builds business equity over time",
            "Equipment Categories: Heavy Machinery (forklifts, cranes, presses, industrial equipment) • Commercial Vehicles (trucks, trailers, delivery fleets) • Warehouse Equipment (racking systems, conveyor systems, packaging machines) • Construction Equipment (excavators, loaders for facility development)"
          ]}
          link="/equipment-finance"
          linkText="Explore Equipment Finance Options"
        />
        <ServiceCard
          icon="ChartLine"
          title="Working Capital for Industrial Operations"
          descriptions={[
            "Manage cash flow for your manufacturing or logistics business with flexible working capital solutions. Fund inventory, cover operational expenses, or bridge payment terms while serving major clients in Yatala's industrial corridor. Access unsecured and secured options tailored to industrial operations.",
            "Benefits: Flexible funding amounts from $10K to $5M+ • Flexible approval for urgent operational requirements • Unsecured options available (no equipment collateral required) • Short-term and long-term solutions to match cash flow"
          ]}
          link="/working-capital-finance"
          linkText="Explore Working Capital Options"
        />
        <ServiceCard
          icon="BuildingWarehouse"
          title="Industrial Property & Facility Finance"
          descriptions={[
            "Finance your industrial facility in Yatala Enterprise Area or surrounding precincts. Whether purchasing a manufacturing plant, warehouse, or distribution centre, access competitive commercial property finance for owner-occupied or investment properties. Leverage Yatala's 25% industrial property value increase over three years.",
            "Benefits: Leverage industrial property growth (25% in 3 years) • Long-term competitive rates for commercial property • Equity release for equipment purchases or expansion • Facility ownership builds long-term business value"
          ]}
          link="/commercial-property-finance"
          linkText="Explore Commercial Property Finance"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

