      <div class="coverage-statement">
        <p>Edgeview Finance serves Queensland manufacturers and logistics businesses with equipment finance specialisation for Yatala Enterprise Area operations. As a local broker, we understand Pacific Motorway corridor industrial dynamics and maintain relationships with over 40 equipment finance specialists to secure competitive rates for manufacturing machinery, logistics equipment, and industrial property acquisitions.</p>
        <p>Book a consultation to discuss your manufacturing or logistics equipment finance needs across Yatala, Stapylton, Pimpama, northern Gold Coast, and Logan industrial corridor.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> 1300 280 895</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> enquiries@edgeviewfinance.com.au</p>
        <p><strong>Service Focus:</strong> Manufacturing facilities and industrial operations, Logistics and warehousing businesses, Heavy industrial and construction companies, Enterprise areas and industrial estates</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-container">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary btn-lg">
          Book Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
